snippet.title: E3 2006 - DDR Universe Trailer (Dance Dance Revolution Universe)
snippet.description:
This is a collection of HD video that was available during the early days of the Xbox 360. 

Some of this content such as the E3 coverage was only available for a very limited time. High definition content was pretty scarce on the internet back in 2006. Even YouTube only supported very badly compressed SD flash video at the time.

For more information on this archive and other rare Xbox 360 content please visit Digiex: https://digiex.net/threads/xbox-video-archive-view-and-download-old-xbox-videos.15348/
